title: Crimes That Shook Australia - Season 1
description:
Crimes That Shook Australia - Season 1

Hosted by Stan Grant and based on the successful series from the UK, Crimes That Shook Britain, this series will look at Australian crimes that shocked our nation. Through the eyes of the people placed right at the heart of the tragedies, the six compelling episodes uncover the biggest crimes to hit our country. Through gripping interviews, drama reconstructions and archival footage, piece together the murders that shocked our nation. The detailed events leading up to the crime, the crime itself and the aftermath will be revealed.

Episodes include:

Ep 1 - Ebony Simpson
Ep 2 - Martin Bryant (The Port Arthur Tragedy)
Ep 3 - Peter Dupas
Ep 4 - Jason Downie
Ep 5 - Katherine Mary Knight
Ep 6 - Derek Percy
